{"type":"message","id":"7505f64b","parentId":"39e59b41","timestamp":"2026-04-03T08:50:28.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a290b7862e3249f7ae0687d1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Tokyo weather today April 3 2026\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 6203,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9f39b9ddc3d3696\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTokyo, Tokyo, Japan Monthly Weather | AccuWeather\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9f39b9ddc3d3696\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/april-weather/226396\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9ecffe365af37cd3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTokyo&#x27;s April 2026 forecast shows <strong>daily high temperatures ranging from 63° to 75°, with overnight lows between 49° and 60°</strong>. The average high for April is 69° with an average low of 55°. AccuWeather&#x27;s monthly forecast extends further ahead ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9ecffe365af37cd3\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.accuweather.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6c77937e01aeb53c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTokyo weather in April 2026 | Tokyo 14 day weather\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6c77937e01aeb53c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=April\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bdbbd26abafdbbb5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nYou can expect about 3 to 8 days of rain in Tokyo during the month of April. It’s a good idea to bring along your umbrella so that you don’t get caught in poor weather. Our weather forecast can give you a great sense of what weather to expect in Tokyo in April 2026.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bdbbd26abafdbbb5\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.weather25.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"989a00de2bb172f3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWeather Tokyo in April 2026: Temperature & Climate\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"989a00de2bb172f3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://en.climate-data.org/asia/japan/tokyo-2442/r/april-4/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2b531c7490324ff8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHere you can find all information about the weather in Tokyo in April: ... The warmest day of April in Tokyo is 30.04, with 20.1°C | 68.1°F, while the coldest day is 03.04, dropping to <strong>4.6°C | 40.2°F</strong>. Early in the month, highs average 15.8°C | 60.4°F, and lows are 5.4°C | 41.7°F. Mid-month ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2b531c7490324ff8\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"en.climate-data.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5df6425099a9e90c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWeather in Tokyo in April 2026 (Tōkyō-to) - detailed Weather Forecast for a month\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5df6425099a9e90c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/april-2026/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8acd929699a0cf20\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDetailed ⚡ Tokyo Weather Forecast for April 2026 – day/night 🌡️ temperatures, precipitations – World-Weather.info\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8acd929699a0cf20\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"world-weather.info\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf5e966f67a888f6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTokyo Weather in April 2026: Pleasant & Warm, Sakura Season\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf5e9