so that you don’t get caught in poor weather. Our weather forecast can give you a great sense of what weather to expect in Tokyo in April 2026.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bdbbd26abafdbbb5\">>>","siteName":"www.weather25.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"989a00de2bb172f3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWeather Tokyo in April 2026: Temperature & Climate\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"989a00de2bb172f3\">>>","url":"https://en.climate-data.org/asia/japan/tokyo-2442/r/april-4/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2b531c7490324ff8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere you can find all information about the weather in Tokyo in April: ... The warmest day of April in Tokyo is 30.04, with 20.1°C | 68.1°F, while the coldest day is 03.04, dropping to <strong>4.6°C | 40.2°F</strong>. Early in the month, highs average 15.8°C | 60.4°F, and lows are 5.4°C | 41.7°F. Mid-month ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2b531c7490324ff8\">>>","siteName":"en.climate-data.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5df6425099a9e90c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWeather in Tokyo in April 2026 (Tōkyō-to) - detailed Weather Forecast for a month\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5df6425099a9e90c\">>>","url":"https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/april-2026/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8acd929699a0cf20\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDetailed ⚡ Tokyo Weather Forecast for April 2026 – day/night 🌡️ temperatures, precipitations – World-Weather.info\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8acd929699a0cf20\">>>","siteName":"world-weather.info"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf5e966f67a888f6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nTokyo Weather in April 2026: Pleasant & Warm, Sakura Season\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf5e966f67a888f6\">>>","url":"https://www.agatetravel.com/japan/tokyo/weather-in-april.html","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"63fe99fc778c7767